WEBVTT

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:30.320
and insisting on dialogue
that doesn't demonize people.

00:10:32.960 --> 00:10:34.640
I'm going to ask you a question.

00:10:35.520 --> 00:10:39.816
I invite you to think about it when
you get home and in the coming days,

00:10:39.840 --> 00:10:42.536
but you have to be honest with yourself.

00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:44.960
It should be easy,
no one else will know it.

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:48.000
The question is this ...

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:52.120
who do you demonize?

00:10:54.600 --> 00:10:58.800
Do you think supporters of American
President Trump are deplorables?